# Project Rules

- **Canonical terms — single source of truth:** `docs/terms.md`. Look up every identifier here before writing it. Typos and unregistered names block merge.
- Canonical governance docs: `README.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `docs/explanation/scope-contract.md`, `docs/explanation/received-document-compliance.md`.
- **NeNe Vault = received-document archive only** (ADR 0009).
- Do NOT add invoice issuance, bank reconciliation, CSV presets, or expense workflows.
- Compliance changes require ADR + professional review when cited by law.
- Issue-driven; English repository docs (ADR 0008); no secrets in git.
- New or renamed identifier → update `docs/terms.md` in the same PR. No exceptions.
